{"id":"sec-postfix-expressions-static-semantics-early-errors","html":"\n      <h1><span class=\"secnum\" id=\"sec-12.4.1\"><a href=\"/sec/sec-postfix-expressions-static-semantics-early-errors.html\" title=\"link to this section\">12.4.1</a></span> Static Semantics:  Early Errors</h1>\n\n      <div class=\"gp\">\n        <div class=\"lhs\"><span class=\"nt\">PostfixExpression</span> <span class=\"geq\">:</span></div>\n        <div class=\"rhs\"><span class=\"nt\">LeftHandSideExpression</span> <code class=\"t\">++</code></div>\n        <div class=\"rhs\"><span class=\"nt\">LeftHandSideExpression</span> <code class=\"t\">--</code></div>\n      </div>\n\n      <ul>\n        <li>\n          <p>It is an early <a href=\"/sec/sec-reference-specification-type.html\">Reference</a> Error if <span style=\"font-family: Times New\n          Roman\">IsValidSimpleAssignmentTarget</span> of <span class=\"nt\">LeftHandSideExpression</span> is <span class=\"value\">false</span>.</p>\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n    "}